  "pageTitle": "重型廢棄物回收參考",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-line-list-page case-line-list-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-bulky-line-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">建築與大型廢棄管線</p>\n        <h1 id=\"construction-bulky-line-title\">重型廢棄物回收參考</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">在開啟完整案例頁面前，請依廢棄物流、流程配置及買家評估 詳情 比較現有Lion One專案。</p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求參考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-line-list-section case-line-section-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-bulky-line-list-title\">\n        <div class=\"case-line-header\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">案件列表</p>\n            <h2 id=\"construction-bulky-line-list-title\">現行的C&amp;D與大型廢棄物箱</h2>\n            <p>每一列將材料情境、流程焦點及 詳情 連結區隔開來，讓買家能快速比較相關專案。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <ol class=\"case-line-list\" aria-label=\"建築與大型廢棄物管線案件清單\">\n          <li class=\"case-line-list-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-line-list-body\">\n              <p class=\"case-line-list-meta\">C&amp;D 廢棄物 |70 t/h Lion One線</p>\n              <h3>C&D 廢棄物利用線</h3>\n              <p>整合破碎、篩分、磁性分離及氣流分離裝置，用於回收骨料及物料回收輸出。</p>\n              <ul class=\"feature-list\">\n                <li>材料：建築與裝飾廢料</li>\n                <li>重點：回收骨料與分離可回收材料</li>\n                <li>詳情 包含：場地狀況、設備範圍、買方背景、影片</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"case-line-list-actions\">\n              <a class=\"card-link\" href=\"/case-studies/construction-bulky-waste-line/construction-waste-utilization\">查看案例 詳情</a>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n\n          <li class=\"case-line-list-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-line-list-body\">\n              <p class=\"case-line-list-meta\">大型廢棄物 |緊湊的預處理佈局</p>\n              <h3>緊湊且大型的廢棄物處理佈局</h3>\n              <p>為需要破碎、氣流分離、可回收回收及打包輸出於一體化的場址提供緊湊的封地方案。</p>\n              <ul class=\"feature-list\">\n                <li>材料：大塊廢棄物與輕質混合廢棄物</li>\n                <li>重點：尺寸縮小、分離與打包介面</li>\n                <li>詳情 包含：轉運站工作流程、設備範圍、買家背景、影片</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"case-line-list-actions\">\n              <a class=\"card-link\" href=\"/case-studies/construction-bulky-waste-line/bulky-waste-processing-layout\">查看案例 詳情</a>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n      </section>\n\n    </main>"
}
